This is OpenGL application solves puzzle with figures and box.
The goal is to put 8 figures into the 2x3x4 box.

Requirements:
* QT4 development libraries
* GLUT development libraries
* qmake

Compilation:
qmake && make

Run:
./glboxsolver

Mouse:
Left drag - rotate figure
Right drag - move figures from center
Middle drag, mouse wheel - zoom

Keys:
A - switch between translucent and regular mode
S - show status
Left, Right - iterate between solutions
Esc - exit
